entries.femaleVariant: That's wrong! It's… it's a sin!
Oh, come on. It's just one measly interface plug.
I can't believe I'm hearing this. From you… You were never like this when we first met.
When we first met, we didn't have kids. It was just us.
We are God's creatures! We have no right to interfere with His work!
It's our son. I just want an easier, better life for him.
Easier? For him, or for you? You wanna be like those friends of yours, like Michael? Like Peter?
